<heading id="D0DF8A6DFFFAC10C7FD7FE9CFC95F718" box="[136,780,302,329]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" reason="4">
1. 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7FFBFE9CFC95F718" authority="(Dozy &amp; Molk.) M. Fleisch." authorityName="M. Fleischer (1923:" authorityYear="1353" baseAuthorityName="Dozy &amp; Molkenboer" baseAuthorityYear="1844" box="[164,780,302,329]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="prostratus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7FFBFE9CFE51F719" bold="true" box="[164,456,302,329]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Glossadelphus prostratus</emphasis>
(Dozy &amp; Molk.) M. Fleisch.
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3326E8AFFFAC10C7FD7FEC4FD13F470" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B973D01FFFAC10C7FD7FEC4FD13F470" blockId="10.[136,1452,374,545]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">
Both 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7F9AFEC4FE47F7C0" box="[197,478,374,400]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="anomalus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7F9AFEC4FE47F7C0" box="[197,478,374,400]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Glossadelphus anomalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion id="49ECF3E3FFFAC10C7D7EFEC4FDEBF7C0" box="[545,626,374,400]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Hainan</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFFAC10C7DDFFEC4FC9CF7C0" author="Tixier, P." box="[640,773,374,400]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="319 - 356" refId="ref9667" refString="Tixier, P. (1988) Le genre Glossadelphus Fleisch. (Sematophyllaceae, Musci) et sa valeur. Nova Hedwigia 46: 319 - 356." type="journal article" year="1988">Tixier 1988</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7C1CFEC4FBBAF7C0" authorityName="J. X. Luo and P. C. Wu" authorityYear="1980" box="[835,1059,374,400]" class="Bryopsida" family="Theliaceae" genus="Myurella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="brevicosta">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7C1CFEC4FBBAF7C0" box="[835,1059,374,400]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Myurella brevicosta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion id="49ECF3E3FFFAC10C7B39FEC4FB2EF7C0" box="[1126,1207,374,400]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Xizang</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFFAC10C7B9AFEC4FA1CF7C0" author="Gao, C. &amp; Cao, T." box="[1221,1413,374,400]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="367 - 375" refId="ref8389" refString="Gao, C. &amp; Cao, T. (1992) Studies of Chinese bryophytes (4). The family Theliaceae (Musci). Journal of the Hattori Botanical Laboratory 71: 367 - 375." type="journal article" year="1992">Gao &amp; Cao 1992</bibRefCitation>
) of 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFFAC10C7FD7FE28FF52F7E4" box="[136,203,410,436]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">China</collectingCountry>
were mistook as 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7ED5FE29FD84F7E4" authorityName="M. Fleischer (1923:" authorityYear="1353" baseAuthorityName="Dozy &amp; Molkenboer" baseAuthorityYear="1844" box="[394,541,411,437]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="prostratus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7ED5FE29FD84F7E4" box="[394,541,411,437]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">G. prostratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and thus the species is once recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFFAC10C7CA3FE28FBA6F7E4" box="[1020,1087,410,436]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">China</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFFAC10C7B13FE28FB6BF7E4" author="Lin, P. - J. &amp; Koponen, T. &amp; Piippo, S." box="[1100,1266,410,436]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="195 - 214" refId="ref8886" refString="Lin, P. - J., Koponen, T. &amp; Piippo, S. (1992) Bryophyte flora of Jianfengling Mts., Hainan Island, China. Bryobrotherea 1: 195 - 214." type="journal article" year="1992">
Lin 
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7B24FE29FB2BF7E4" box="[1147,1202,410,436]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">et al.</emphasis>
1992
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFFAC10C7BA3FE28FA39F7E4" author="Jia, Y. &amp; He, S." box="[1276,1440,410,437]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="1 - 525" refId="ref8775" refString="Jia, Y. &amp; He, S. (2013) Species Catalogue of China. Science Press, Beijing, pp. 1 - 525. [in Chinese]" type="book chapter" year="2013">Jia &amp; He 2013</bibRefCitation>
). However, our study indicates that 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7D54FE0DFD02F788" box="[523,667,446,473]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="anomalus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7D54FE0DFD02F788" box="[523,667,446,473]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">G. anomalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7D8CFE0DFCF4F788" authorityName="J. X. Luo and P. C. Wu" authorityYear="1980" box="[723,877,446,472]" class="Bryopsida" family="Theliaceae" genus="Myurella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="brevicosta">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7D8CFE0DFCF4F788" box="[723,877,446,472]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">M. brevicosta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are not identical with 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7B33FE0DFA98F788" authorityName="M. Fleischer (1923:" authorityYear="1353" baseAuthorityName="Dozy &amp; Molkenboer" baseAuthorityYear="1844" box="[1132,1281,447,473]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="prostratus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7B33FE0DFA98F788" box="[1132,1281,447,473]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">G. prostratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7FD7FE50FEA3F7AC" authorityName="Mitten" authorityYear="1868" box="[136,314,482,508]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Ectropothecium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7FD7FE50FEA3F7AC" box="[136,314,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Ectropothecium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7E2BFE51FE63F7AC" authorityName="L. E. Anderson" authorityYear="1980" box="[372,506,483,508]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Bryocrumia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7E2BFE51FE63F7AC" box="[372,506,483,508]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Bryocrumia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, respectively (See sections 3.1 and 2.1 above for details). Therefore, 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFFAC10C7A4AFE51FA32F7AC" authorityName="M. Fleischer (1923:" authorityYear="1353" baseAuthorityName="Dozy &amp; Molkenboer" baseAuthorityYear="1844" box="[1301,1451,483,509]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="prostratus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFFAC10C7A4AFE51FA32F7AC" box="[1301,1451,483,509]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">G. prostratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be excluded from moss flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFFAC10C7D60FDB4FD1FF470" box="[575,646,518,544]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
